quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  51,52,"Saa ara nso na AsomafoÕĽ a wÕĽbaa amanfoÕĽ a wÕĽdii wÕĽn anim kan no hÕĽ no, wÕĽka kyerőĶőĶ wÕĽn sőĶ wÕĽyőĶ nkoyaayifoÕĽ anaasőĶ wÕĽn abobÕĽ adam."
  51,53,"(TetefoÕĽ no) na wÕĽtuu wÕĽn fo saa anaa? Daabi, wÕĽn ara yőĶ nnipa a wÕĽto mmara."
  51,54,"Enti twe woho fri wÕĽn ho, na yőĶmmÕĽ wo soboÕĽ."
  51,55,"Na tufo, efrisőĶ afutuo no ho wÕĽ mfasoÕĽ ma agyidiefoÕĽ no."
  51,56,"∆źnyőĶ hwee ho nti na MebÕĽÕĽ Jinn ne nnipa, na mmom (MebÕĽÕĽ wÕĽn) sőĶ wÕĽ‚Äônsom Me."
  51,57,"MennhwehwőĶ akÕĽnhoma biara wÕĽ wÕĽn hÕĽ, na mennhwehwőĶ nso sőĶ wÕĽ‚Äôma Me biribi nni."
  51,58,"NokorőĶ sőĶ, NyankopÕĽn ne ∆ÜkyőĶ adeőĶ Hene; OtumfoÕĽ ∆ÜhoÕĽdenfoÕĽ paa ne no."
  51,59,"NokorőĶ sőĶ, wÕĽn a wÕĽ‚Äôdi bÕĽne no wÕĽ bÕĽne so asotwee tesőĶ wÕĽn a wÕĽ‚Äôdii kan wÕĽ wÕĽn anim no ara pőĶpőĶőĶpőĶ; enti őĶmma wÕĽn mpre ho sőĶ Memfa (asotwee no) mmra."
  51,60,"Enti due nka wÕĽn a wÕĽ‚Äôpo (nokorőĶ) no wÕĽ wÕĽn Da a yahyőĶ wÕĽn ho bÕĽ no mu."
  52,1,"Mede BepÕĽ Tuur (a Mene Mose kasaa wÕĽ soÕĽ),"
  52,2,"Ne Nwoma a yatwerőĶ-"
  52,3,"WÕĽ nwoma a yatrőĶ mu soÕĽ,"
  52,4,"Ne Efie no a ( Soro abÕĽfoÕĽ) twa ho hyia,"
  52,5,"Ne (ÕĽsoro) nkurusoÕĽ a yapagya,"
  52,6,"Ne ÕĽpo a nsuo ayiri ayőĶ mma (anaasőĶ ÕĽpo a egya bőĶtÕĽ mu wÕĽ Atemmuda) no di nse sőĶ:"
  52,7,"‚ÄúNokorőĶ, wo Wura NyankopÕĽn asotwee no besi ampa."
  52,8,"Na enni obia obetumi asi ano kwan."
  52,9,"∆źda a ÕĽsoro bőĶwoso nwosoeőĶ paa no,"
  52,10,"Na mmepÕĽ betutu afri hÕĽ tutu paa no,"
  52,11,"Saa Da no due nka wÕĽn a wÕĽfaa nokorőĶ no atorŠīźs‘Ďm no,"
  52,12,"WÕĽn a wÕĽde ahuhudeőĶ na őĶgye wÕĽn ani no."
  52,13,"∆źda no a yőĶbepia wÕĽn wÕĽ ÕĽhyőĶ so akÕĽ Amanehunu gya no mu no,"
  52,14,"(YőĶbőĶka akyerőĶ wÕĽn sőĶ): ‚ÄúOgya no a na moka sőĶ őĶyőĶ nkontompo no nie."